Software package installation tools:

pconf    Runs `./configure` with configurations
pmake    Runs `make` with configurations
pclean   Removes unwanted files
pp	 Converts a generical FHS-compliant path into a one following fh.conf, without support for prefixes
	 (the second p stands for path)
pfh	 Extract a value of the directory table after configurations
	 (fh stands for filesystem hierarchy)

